{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 11","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Naučili ste prvu grupu početnih konsonanti, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">m</span>, na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span>. Sada ćete videti kako se ove početne konsonante kombinuju sa jednostavnim vokalom koje ste ranije naučili da biste stvorili Pinyin i generisali kineske znakove.</p>\n<p>Kada ukucate tačan Pinyin zajedno sa brojevima tona, unos/ulaz Pinyin-u Hanzi će se pretvoriti u znakove.</p>\n<p>Na ovom koraku, ne morate da brinete o razumevanju značenja ovih karaktera. Cilj je samo da steknete iskustvo kako vam Pinyin pomaže da unesete i prepoznate ta slova/karaktere.</p>\n<p>Zapamti da proširiš deo opisa ili da proveriš značenje reči ako želiš da učiš.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk i dovršite reč koja je navedena ispod. Tačni slogovi će biti konvertovani u kineske znakove.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Prva sloga spaja početnu konsonantu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">p</span> sa vokalom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, i koristi prvi ton, koji je visok i ravan. Druga sloga spaja početnu konsonantu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">f</span> sa vokalom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, i koristi četvrti ton, koji naglo pada.</p>\n<p><ruby>批复<rp>(</rp><rt>pī fù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> znači \"zvaničan odgovor\". Često se koristi u kontekstu posla ili vlade, na primer kada zahtev ili dokument dobije zvaničan odgovor.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","lang":"zh-CN","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-11"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"批复 (pī fù)","feedback":"<p>Ova reč povezuje slog <span class=\"highlighted-text\">pī</span> sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">fù</span>.</p>"}]},"inputType":"pinyin-to-hanzi","tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company3-reception.png","characters":[{"character":"Wang Hua","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_initials.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":208.12,"finishTimestamp":209.99},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.87,"dialogue":{"text":"<ruby>批复<rp>(</rp><rt>pī fù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Wang Hua","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.37,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-learn-initials","dashedName":"task-11","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-pinyin","module":"zh-a1-module-initials-and-finals","block":"zh-a1-learn-initials","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-12","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-10","id":"655b75fa252a5490ca70ca39","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-initials/task-11"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}